  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i>Welcome to the digital world of The Windzen Hero!</i></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This fast paced run and gun action-platformer takes place in the mind of an advanced computer system. Troubled by a feeling of danger that he can't shake a little worker named Hero asks his DirexOS Computer to render live training courses in the Holographic Chamber. When Hero steps inside he realizes that he may have been given more than he bargained for.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Can Hero conquer Ten challenging stages and a climactic Final Battle? That's all up to you!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i>Re:Made - Re:Designed - Re:HERO!</i></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/777540/extras/4b84e87f164ba761216c33777f3d9fe8.avif?t=1752451209\" width=800 height=779 /></span> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/777540/extras/f2cf5601bd01c6401a20315f9870b7cd.avif?t=1752451209\" width=800 height=776 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/777540/extras/1ff04cba41e3cd2c6bc5cab394212f74.avif?t=1752451209\" width=800 height=1027 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/777540/extras/e12115d98275b86005c27047f3843817.avif?t=1752451209\" width=800 height=779 /></span> </p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i>Welcome to the digital world of The Windzen Hero!</i></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This fast paced run and gun action-platformer takes place in the mind of an advanced computer system. Troubled by a feeling of danger that he can't shake a little worker named Hero asks his DirexOS Computer to render live training courses in the Holographic Chamber. When Hero steps inside he realizes that he may have been given more than he bargained for.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Can Hero conquer Ten challenging stages and a climactic Final Battle? That's all up to you!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i>Re:Made - Re:Designed - Re:HERO!</i></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/777540/extras/4b84e87f164ba761216c33777f3d9fe8.avif?t=1752451209\" width=800 height=779 /></span> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/777540/extras/f2cf5601bd01c6401a20315f9870b7cd.avif?t=1752451209\" width=800 height=776 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/777540/extras/1ff04cba41e3cd2c6bc5cab394212f74.avif?t=1752451209\" width=800 height=1027 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/777540/extras/e12115d98275b86005c27047f3843817.avif?t=1752451209\" width=800 height=779 /></span> </p>",
